{
  "video_id": "bUjrtRQ64ek",
  "title": "What happened when we tested thousands of abandoned rape kits in Detroit | Kym Worthy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13000.0,
      "end_time": 19400.0,
      "text": "In 2009, in August, my office weathered two major scandals."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19800.0,
      "end_time": 24856.0,
      "text": "The first was the arrest, trying and conviction"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24880.0,
      "end_time": 28759.0,
      "text": "and subsequent incarceration of Detroit's very popular mayor."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 29880.0,
      "end_time": 36400.0,
      "text": "The second caused the Detroit police department crime lab to be closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 36800.0,
      "end_time": 39239.0,
      "text": "I thought nothing else could go wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 41000.0,
      "end_time": 42256.0,
      "text": "And then the phone rang."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 42280.0,
      "end_time": 43656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 43680.0,
      "end_time": 47376.0,
      "text": "It was the deputy chief of my special victim's unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 47400.0,
      "end_time": 50416.0,
      "text": "who was breathless on the other end of the line."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 50440.0,
      "end_time": 55720.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Boss, you are never going to believe what I just saw.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 57000.0,
      "end_time": 59736.0,
      "text": "I had a sinking feeling in the pit of my stomach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59760.0,
      "end_time": 62536.0,
      "text": "because I knew instinctively"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62560.0,
      "end_time": 67376.0,
      "text": "that Detroit was getting ready to suffer its third major scandal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 67400.0,
      "end_time": 69720.0,
      "text": "in just over one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 71280.0,
      "end_time": 76296.0,
      "text": "He told me that he had just visited what he thought was an abandoned warehouse"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 76319.0,
      "end_time": 79120.0,
      "text": "where the Detroit police department was storing evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 80000.0,
      "end_time": 86816.0,
      "text": "Inside were 11,341 abandoned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 86840.0,
      "end_time": 88840.0,
      "text": "untested rape kits."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 89440.0,
      "end_time": 92440.0,
      "text": "Some of them went back to the 1980s."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 93280.0,
      "end_time": 97200.0,
      "text": "And some of them now are over 40 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 97960.0,
      "end_time": 102455.0,
      "text": "These kits were spilling out of large, black garbage bags"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 102480.0,
      "end_time": 104800.0,
      "text": "and empty oil drums."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 105440.0,
      "end_time": 108176.0,
      "text": "Each kit represented a victim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 109656.0,
      "text": "mostly a female,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 109680.0,
      "end_time": 112920.0,
      "text": "that had suffered a violent sexual assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 113880.0,
      "end_time": 120416.0,
      "text": "Each of them voluntarily endured an hours-long rape kit process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 120440.0,
      "end_time": 124440.0,
      "text": "with the hopes that as a result of that they would find their perpetrator."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 125960.0,
      "end_time": 131656.0,
      "text": "And unbeknownst to all of them, all 11,341,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 131680.0,
      "end_time": 133600.0,
      "text": "those kits were never tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 135480.0,
      "end_time": 138215.0,
      "text": "I cannot even begin to describe -- oh!"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 138240.0,
      "end_time": 140960.0,
      "text": "And by the way, before I move on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 140120.0,
      "end_time": 142416.0,
      "text": "in the interim of those 40 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 142440.0,
      "end_time": 147280.0,
      "text": "those perpetrators were allowed to continue to offend with impunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 148640.0,
      "end_time": 155359.0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you or describe to you how outraged, mad and angry I was."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 156520.0,
      "end_time": 159296.0,
      "text": "I myself was a victim of sexual assault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 159320.0,
      "end_time": 161959.0,
      "text": "back many decades ago, when I was in law school."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 162720.0,
      "end_time": 167840.0,
      "text": "I also am the mother of three girls, a 21-year-old and nine-year-old twins."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 169400.0,
      "end_time": 174176.0,
      "text": "I was even more horrified to learn -- if I could be more horrified --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 174200.0,
      "end_time": 176119.0,
      "text": "that the oldest of those kits --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 177240.0,
      "end_time": 180560.0,
      "text": "one of the oldest of those kits -- belonged to an eight-year-old girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 181400.0,
      "end_time": 184760.0,
      "text": "I'm going to tell you her story, but I'm going to call her Natasha."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 185840.0,
      "end_time": 192176.0,
      "text": "On January 2, 1990, Natasha was at home and a man knocked on her door."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 192200.0,
      "end_time": 194416.0,
      "text": "This man was familiar with her neighborhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 194440.0,
      "end_time": 197496.0,
      "text": "and was familiar with the comings and goings of her family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 197520.0,
      "end_time": 199800.0,
      "text": "but Natasha did not know him."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 200720.0,
      "end_time": 205616.0,
      "text": "He told her that her grandmother, the only mother that she had ever known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 205640.0,
      "end_time": 207535.0,
      "text": "had been in a terrible accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 207560.0,
      "end_time": 210720.0,
      "text": "and was laying on a couch in his house, calling for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 211720.0,
      "end_time": 216696.0,
      "text": "Terrified that Natasha was going to lose her grandmother, she went with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 216720.0,
      "end_time": 219776.0,
      "text": "But of course, we all know her grandmother was not there."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 223736.0,
      "text": "Once he had isolated Natasha, who was eight years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 223760.0,
      "end_time": 226296.0,
      "text": "he began to rape her violently."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 226320.0,
      "end_time": 230696.0,
      "text": "He raped her with his mouth, his fingers and his penis."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 230720.0,
      "end_time": 233560.0,
      "text": "And he even forced his penis into her mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 234880.0,
      "end_time": 238160.0,
      "text": "When he was done, he ordered Natasha to get dressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 238400.0,
      "end_time": 239696.0,
      "text": "he got dressed himself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 239720.0,
      "end_time": 242376.0,
      "text": "and he put a blindfold across her head."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 242400.0,
      "end_time": 246200.0,
      "text": "And walked her to a factory area on the edge of the neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 247120.0,
      "end_time": 249656.0,
      "text": "He asked her if she knew -- he removed the blindfold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 249680.0,
      "end_time": 252176.0,
      "text": "and asked her if she knew how to get home from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 252200.0,
      "end_time": 255640.0,
      "text": "And when she indicated that she did, he let her go and he walked off."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 256920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260376.00000000003,
      "text": "Natasha's rape was reported immediately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 260399.0,
      "end_time": 262000.0,
      "text": "and a rape kit was done."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 262960.0,
      "end_time": 268799.0,
      "text": "Now, the rape kit process terrifies and traumatizes adult women."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 269720.0,
      "end_time": 273216.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine what it was like for a little second-grader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 273240.0,
      "end_time": 276816.0,
      "text": "who still wore pigtails and still believed in Santa Claus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 276840.0,
      "end_time": 278440.0,
      "text": "going through this exam?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 280200.0,
      "end_time": 284135.0,
      "text": "Natasha's kit sat on the shelf in that abandoned warehouse"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 284160.0,
      "end_time": 286880.0,
      "text": "for 26 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 289520.0,
      "end_time": 291856.0,
      "text": "Pamela, 19 years old --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 291880.0,
      "end_time": 294216.0,
      "text": "I'll call her Pamela, that's not her real name --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 294240.0,
      "end_time": 296976.0,
      "text": "nineteen years old, was walking down the street"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 297000.0,
      "end_time": 299736.0,
      "text": "after she had come from visiting her boyfriend."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 299760.0,
      "end_time": 302135.0,
      "text": "She was grabbed from behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 302160.0,
      "end_time": 305600.0,
      "text": "and she felt what she thought was a gun, in her side."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 306320.0,
      "end_time": 308736.0,
      "text": "She was taken to an abandoned house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 308760.0,
      "end_time": 312480.0,
      "text": "to a bedroom in that house, that was filled with trash."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 313960.0,
      "end_time": 315880.0,
      "text": "Every time she tried to resist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 316960.0,
      "end_time": 320800.0,
      "text": "he would hit her about the face and the head."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 321120.0,
      "end_time": 324976.0,
      "text": "He violently raped her on the floor of that bedroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 325000.0,
      "end_time": 326960.0,
      "text": "that was filled with garbage."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 329640.0,
      "end_time": 331416.0,
      "text": "When he was done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 331440.0,
      "end_time": 333296.0,
      "text": "he put on his clothes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 333320.0,
      "end_time": 336400.0,
      "text": "he stole her money, and he just walked away."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 339600.0,
      "end_time": 342240.0,
      "text": "Pamela also reported her rape right away."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 344280.0,
      "end_time": 346176.0,
      "text": "She also had a rape kit done."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 346200.0,
      "end_time": 351000.0,
      "text": "And like Natasha's, her kit sat on the shelf for 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 352520.0,
      "end_time": 357856.0,
      "text": "Now, criminals, like people who raped Natasha and Pamela,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 357880.0,
      "end_time": 359880.0,
      "text": "often leave their DNA at a crime scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 360880.0,
      "end_time": 365480.0,
      "text": "But for a rape victim, their body is the crime scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 366760.0,
      "end_time": 370976.0,
      "text": "So many elect to go through this hours-long rape kit process"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 371000.0,
      "end_time": 376856.0,
      "text": "that requires every inch and orifice of a victim's body"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 376880.0,
      "end_time": 381240.0,
      "text": "to be combed, swabbed and photographed."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 382360.0,
      "end_time": 385840.0,
      "text": "All right after a violent sexual assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 386800.0,
      "end_time": 389856.0,
      "text": "The reason that most people do this, who have a rape kit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 389880.0,
      "end_time": 393496.0,
      "text": "is because they want the forensic scientists to study that rape kit."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 393520.0,
      "end_time": 396335.0,
      "text": "And hopefully come up with a genetic profile"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 396360.0,
      "end_time": 398800.0,
      "text": "that will help identify their perpetrator."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 399680.0,
      "end_time": 402776.0,
      "text": "Once forensic scientists come up with this genetic profile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 406576.0,
      "text": "they enter it into CODIS, hopefully have a match."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 406600.0,
      "end_time": 411896.0,
      "text": "CODIS is filled with DNA profiles of people who are arrested"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 411920.0,
      "end_time": 415440.0,
      "text": "and/or convicted of certain prescribed offenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 416840.0,
      "end_time": 419856.0,
      "text": "If in fact a profile is made and entered into CODIS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 419880.0,
      "end_time": 423120.0,
      "text": "it can help identify a perpetrator in the matter of minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 423760.0,
      "end_time": 428800.0,
      "text": "CODIS stands for Combined DNA Index System."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 431160.0,
      "end_time": 433360.0,
      "text": "Now, how did we get here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 434560.0,
      "end_time": 436720.0,
      "text": "Detroit had no money."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 438240.0,
      "end_time": 440576.0,
      "text": "It cost, at that time that these kits were found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 440600.0,
      "end_time": 445576.0,
      "text": "up to 1,500 dollars per kit to have it tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 445600.0,
      "end_time": 448336.0,
      "text": "So, you do the math about how much that was going to cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 448360.0,
      "end_time": 450616.0,
      "text": "In addition to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 450640.0,
      "end_time": 454416.0,
      "text": "within four years of these kits being found in 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 454440.0,
      "end_time": 459560.0,
      "text": "Detroit would be the largest municipality in the history of the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 459800.0,
      "end_time": 460479.0,
      "text": "to declare bankruptcy."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 461800.0,
      "end_time": 463936.0,
      "text": "We didn't know what we were going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 463960.0,
      "end_time": 465176.0,
      "text": "But not only that."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 465200.0,
      "end_time": 469736.0,
      "text": "As we began to study and investigate how this possibly could have happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 469760.0,
      "end_time": 473599.0,
      "text": "we discovered there were other issues besides just financial ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 474880.0,
      "end_time": 480135.0,
      "text": "During the course of these decades where these kits sat in that warehouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 480160.0,
      "end_time": 484496.0,
      "text": "we discovered there had been multiple changes of police leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 484520.0,
      "end_time": 487775.0,
      "text": "with different priorities and different agendas."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 487800.0,
      "end_time": 492160.0,
      "text": "There was woefully inadequate training for sex crimes officers"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 492400.0,
      "end_time": 493840.0,
      "text": "in the police department in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 494640.0,
      "end_time": 497895.0,
      "text": "They were chronically understaffed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 497920.0,
      "end_time": 500960.0,
      "text": "and they had other resource issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 500120.0,
      "end_time": 505376.0,
      "text": "And there was perpetual victim blaming"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 505400.0,
      "end_time": 508936.0,
      "text": "when these victims came to report their crimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 508960.0,
      "end_time": 510599.0,
      "text": "That's the rape culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 511360.0,
      "end_time": 513816.0,
      "text": "And because of this victim blaming"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 513840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516296.00000000006,
      "text": "of someone that had been violently assaulted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 516320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518656.00000000006,
      "text": "some of these victim were even ridiculed"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 518679.0,
      "end_time": 521760.0,
      "text": "into not continuing to proceed with their case."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 522600.0,
      "end_time": 528200.0,
      "text": "The bottom line is, that 11,341 rape kits sat on that shelf."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 530440.0,
      "end_time": 532296.0,
      "text": "I wanted transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 532320.0,
      "end_time": 537576.0,
      "text": "I asked myself: How in the world can we stop this from spreading?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 537600.0,
      "end_time": 541176.0,
      "text": "I don't want to go through all this work and five, 10 years down the line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 541200.0,
      "end_time": 542640.0,
      "text": "figure we have the same issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 543440.0,
      "end_time": 547960.0,
      "text": "At that time, police officers had the sole discretion"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 547120.0,
      "end_time": 549736.0,
      "text": "about whether and when and if"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 549760.0,
      "end_time": 552336.0,
      "text": "they were going to submit the rape kits for testing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 552360.0,
      "end_time": 554736.0,
      "text": "any rape kit in their jurisdiction -- for testing."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 554760.0,
      "end_time": 555976.0,
      "text": "That had to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 556000.0,
      "end_time": 558696.0,
      "text": "We had to take that discretion away from police officers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 558720.0,
      "end_time": 560336.0,
      "text": "and pass state laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 560360.0,
      "end_time": 565560.0,
      "text": "to ensure that every rape kit released by the victim to law enforcement"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 565800.0,
      "end_time": 567360.0,
      "text": "is tested immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 568720.0,
      "end_time": 571176.0,
      "text": "I also knew that there had to be some kind of system"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 571200.0,
      "end_time": 575216.0,
      "text": "to keep everybody honest and to keep everybody accountable, put in place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 575240.0,
      "end_time": 578760.0,
      "text": "where we knew where these rape kits were, at any given time."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 580280.0,
      "end_time": 581520.0,
      "text": "The answer was simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 582440.0,
      "end_time": 586216.0,
      "text": "Think about all of the hundreds of thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 586240.0,
      "end_time": 588576.0,
      "text": "and perhaps millions of packages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 588600.0,
      "end_time": 591440.0,
      "text": "that are moved by a logistics company every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 593320.0,
      "end_time": 595656.0,
      "text": "They are scanned and tracked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 595680.0,
      "end_time": 598175.0,
      "text": "and they know where they are, at every bend and turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 598200.0,
      "end_time": 600616.0,
      "text": "from the time that they're stored in the warehouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 600640.0,
      "end_time": 605360.0,
      "text": "until the time that that package arrives on the purchaser's front steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 606840.0,
      "end_time": 608680.0,
      "text": "Why couldn't we do that for rape kits?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 609600.0,
      "end_time": 613160.0,
      "text": "I had no desire to reinvent the wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 613400.0,
      "end_time": 614560.0,
      "text": "So I contacted UPS."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 616400.0,
      "end_time": 621160.0,
      "text": "UPS, within two weeks -- two weeks --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 621400.0,
      "end_time": 623415.0,
      "text": "of our first meeting with UPS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 623440.0,
      "end_time": 626536.0,
      "text": "they had come up with a major plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 626560.0,
      "end_time": 628616.0,
      "text": "where they involved all the stakeholders --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 628640.0,
      "end_time": 631536.0,
      "text": "the police officers, the prosecutors, the medical facilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 631560.0,
      "end_time": 633856.0,
      "text": "the forensic nurses, the hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 633880.0,
      "end_time": 636576.0,
      "text": "the lab personnel and the victim advocates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 636600.0,
      "end_time": 639680.0,
      "text": "could know where the rape kits were at any given time."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 640600.0,
      "end_time": 643160.0,
      "text": "They sent a team of experts out"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 643400.0,
      "end_time": 646550.0,
      "text": "and fanned the Detroit area, talked to all the stakeholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 646800.0,
      "end_time": 647696.0,
      "text": "and developed a plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 647720.0,
      "end_time": 649416.0,
      "text": "and studied the life of a rape kit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 649440.0,
      "end_time": 651936.0,
      "text": "from the time the rape kit was collected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 651960.0,
      "end_time": 654296.0,
      "text": "through to the time that it was tested in the lab"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 654320.0,
      "end_time": 656576.0,
      "text": "and returned to the police personnel."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 656600.0,
      "end_time": 659776.0,
      "text": "They also developed a web-based portal"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 659800.0,
      "end_time": 663496.0,
      "text": "that all the stakeholders could look into and see where any given rape kit was"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 663520.0,
      "end_time": 665295.0,
      "text": "at any given time."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 665320.0,
      "end_time": 667256.0,
      "text": "UPS had the technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 667280.0,
      "end_time": 670336.0,
      "text": "UPS knew how to use that technology to solve our problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 670360.0,
      "end_time": 671800.0,
      "text": "and we didn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 673400.0,
      "end_time": 675496.0,
      "text": "We launched -- we, we --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 675520.0,
      "end_time": 677536.0,
      "text": "UPS and the prosecutor's office --"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 677560.0,
      "end_time": 678776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 678800.0,
      "end_time": 681839.0,
      "text": "launched this pilot program in Detroit."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 682800.0,
      "end_time": 688575.0,
      "text": "And we started this process on January 28, 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 688600.0,
      "end_time": 693560.0,
      "text": "through to May 25 of 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 693800.0,
      "end_time": 694696.0,
      "text": "And during that period of time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 694720.0,
      "end_time": 697136.0,
      "text": "remember, we're not dealing with the ones we found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 697160.0,
      "end_time": 698976.0,
      "text": "because they'd already been stored --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 699000.0,
      "end_time": 702696.0,
      "text": "we're dealing with any new kit that came in as of January 28, 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 702720.0,
      "end_time": 705616.0,
      "text": "And we knew where that rape kit was."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 705640.0,
      "end_time": 711336.0,
      "text": "For the 16 months of this project, we didn't lose a single rape kit."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 711360.0,
      "end_time": 712576.0,
      "text": "Not a single one."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 712600.0,
      "end_time": 714560.0,
      "text": "We knew where they all were."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 714800.0,
      "end_time": 720496.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 720520.0,
      "end_time": 723415.0,
      "text": "This project went on until the state of Michigan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 723440.0,
      "end_time": 725896.0,
      "text": "the elected officials in state government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 725920.0,
      "end_time": 729160.0,
      "text": "took notice of everything that UPS was doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 729400.0,
      "end_time": 730976.0,
      "text": "And everything that my office was doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 731000.0,
      "end_time": 734936.0,
      "text": "And they decided that they were going to use state funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 734960.0,
      "end_time": 737576.0,
      "text": "to develop a state-wide tracking system."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 737600.0,
      "end_time": 740440.0,
      "text": "Not in just Detroit, but state-wide tracking system."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 741520.0,
      "end_time": 744550.0,
      "text": "Hopefully, that system will be up and running soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 744800.0,
      "end_time": 746960.0,
      "text": "But I loved working with UPS."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 746120.0,
      "end_time": 749456.0,
      "text": "I loved their innovation, I loved how fast they worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 749480.0,
      "end_time": 754160.0,
      "text": "I loved their unorthodox approach to ideas to solve an everyday, common problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 754400.0,
      "end_time": 756319.0,
      "text": "whose solution should be simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 758760.0,
      "end_time": 761656.0,
      "text": "So, after working with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 761680.0,
      "end_time": 764175.0,
      "text": "I knew that even with one company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 764200.0,
      "end_time": 766560.0,
      "text": "working on one issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 766800.0,
      "end_time": 767800.0,
      "text": "the progress that could be made."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 769480.0,
      "end_time": 773760.0,
      "text": "We've been at this now for nine years."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 775360.0,
      "end_time": 778136.0,
      "text": "And it was nine years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 778160.0,
      "end_time": 781719.0,
      "text": "that we rescued those rape kits from the warehouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 782880.0,
      "end_time": 785400.0,
      "text": "That warehouse has since been torn down."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 786320.0,
      "end_time": 789536.0,
      "text": "But all of the kits have either been tested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 789560.0,
      "end_time": 791599.0,
      "text": "or are in the final stages of being tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 792680.0,
      "end_time": 794376.0,
      "text": "We still have a lot of work to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 794400.0,
      "end_time": 798616.0,
      "text": "in terms of investigation and prosecution of those cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 798640.0,
      "end_time": 802656.0,
      "text": "but our rape kit issue, in terms of testing, is done."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 802680.0,
      "end_time": 805760.0,
      "text": "As of June 28, 2018,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 806880.0,
      "end_time": 812200.0,
      "text": "our CODIS hits have showed us and identified 2,600 suspects."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 813360.0,
      "end_time": 820120.0,
      "text": "We have identified 861 serial rapists."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 820800.0,
      "end_time": 822550.0,
      "text": "Just within this project."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 822800.0,
      "end_time": 826536.0,
      "text": "That means 861 potential defendants"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 826560.0,
      "end_time": 829400.0,
      "text": "that have raped within the project two or more times."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 830160.0,
      "end_time": 836400.0,
      "text": "And 50 to 75 of them have raped 10 to 15 times a piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 836840.0,
      "end_time": 839400.0,
      "text": "In one city, in one state."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 841160.0,
      "end_time": 844376.0,
      "text": "Also, the CODIS results that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 844400.0,
      "end_time": 846256.0,
      "text": "have tentacles to crime scenes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 846280.0,
      "end_time": 850696.0,
      "text": "have linkages in 40 states in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 850720.0,
      "end_time": 855976.0,
      "text": "Forty of the 50 states have tentacles to our crime testing of these rape kits."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 856000.0,
      "end_time": 858576.0,
      "text": "From Alaska to Florida"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 858600.0,
      "end_time": 862336.0,
      "text": "and from Maine to the most southern parts of California."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 862360.0,
      "end_time": 866200.0,
      "text": "A sea to shining sea, string of CODIS hits."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 868840.0,
      "end_time": 871480.0,
      "text": "Natasha is now 36 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 872720.0,
      "end_time": 876976.0,
      "text": "When she heard about the work that we were doing with the rape kits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 877000.0,
      "end_time": 880856.0,
      "text": "she contacted my office, the Wayne County prosecutor's office."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 880880.0,
      "end_time": 883560.0,
      "text": "Her kit was eventually tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 883800.0,
      "end_time": 886136.0,
      "text": "And it had identified Paul Warwick."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 886160.0,
      "end_time": 890415.0,
      "text": "In the interim, Paul Warwick had raped two more women."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 890440.0,
      "end_time": 892760.0,
      "text": "One in the state of Colorado."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 893920.0,
      "end_time": 898896.0,
      "text": "Paul Warwick is now serving a sentence in the Michigan Department of Corrections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 898920.0,
      "end_time": 901575.0,
      "text": "in prison, of 15 to 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 901600.0,
      "end_time": 908456.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 908480.0,
      "end_time": 911256.0,
      "text": "Pamela's kit was also tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 911280.0,
      "end_time": 914696.0,
      "text": "And her kit led to the identification -- her CODIS hit on her kit --"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 914720.0,
      "end_time": 917400.0,
      "text": "led to the identification of Bernard Peterson."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 918400.0,
      "end_time": 924680.0,
      "text": "In the interim, Bernard Peterson raped 10 more women."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 925920.0,
      "end_time": 928976.0,
      "text": "Each of those women had a rape kit done."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 929000.0,
      "end_time": 933800.0,
      "text": "And each of those women's rape kits sat on that shelf next to Pamela's."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 934600.0,
      "end_time": 936520.0,
      "text": "For a varying number of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 938000.0,
      "end_time": 940576.0,
      "text": "Bernard Peterson is now serving a sentence"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 940600.0,
      "end_time": 942656.0,
      "text": "in the Michigan Department of Corrections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 942680.0,
      "end_time": 944856.0,
      "text": "concurrently -- that means at the same time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 944880.0,
      "end_time": 949160.0,
      "text": "of 60 to 90 years, and 90 years to 125 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 949400.0,
      "end_time": 950616.0,
      "text": "for the rapes that he committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 950640.0,
      "end_time": 956856.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 956880.0,
      "end_time": 960560.0,
      "text": "We still have a lot of work to be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 960800.0,
      "end_time": 963456.0,
      "text": "And we desperately need the help of the private sector."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 963480.0,
      "end_time": 965856.0,
      "text": "We need the help of the tech industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 965880.0,
      "end_time": 969216.0,
      "text": "To help us develop -- not help us, we want them to develop --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 969240.0,
      "end_time": 971496.0,
      "text": "information management systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 971520.0,
      "end_time": 973776.0,
      "text": "so we can all talk to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 973800.0,
      "end_time": 975695.0,
      "text": "and stop these perpetrators"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 975720.0,
      "end_time": 978360.0,
      "text": "from raping and maiming and killing with impunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 979600.0,
      "end_time": 981536.0,
      "text": "We also need help from those of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 981560.0,
      "end_time": 985295.0,
      "text": "with marketing and advertisement backgrounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 985320.0,
      "end_time": 987776.0,
      "text": "We need you, desperately we need you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 987800.0,
      "end_time": 993550.0,
      "text": "to develop campaigns for our children and other people to listen to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 993800.0,
      "end_time": 997376.0,
      "text": "so we can stop the culture, change the culture of rape victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 997400.0,
      "end_time": 1001720.0,
      "text": "being too afraid to come forward because of what may happen to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1004360.0,
      "end_time": 1007616.0,
      "text": "UPS was one company, as I said."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1007640.0,
      "end_time": 1009816.0,
      "text": "They helped us with their innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1009840.0,
      "end_time": 1014960.0,
      "text": "and they revolutionized the way that we can track rape kits."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1014120.0,
      "end_time": 1018296.0,
      "text": "Every single aspect of our lives is tracked."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1018320.0,
      "end_time": 1021216.0,
      "text": "Every like, every mood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1021240.0,
      "end_time": 1024976.0,
      "text": "shopping history, browsing history, reading history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1025000.0,
      "end_time": 1029400.0,
      "text": "our entire web history is tracked these days."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1030240.0,
      "end_time": 1035496.0,
      "text": "What if we could track the activities and the comings and goings"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1035520.0,
      "end_time": 1037336.0,
      "text": "of criminals who commit crimes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1037359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1039721.9999999999,
      "text": "Just like people track every aspect of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1041400.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1045454.0000000001,
      "text": "In 2015, the Obama White House"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1045480.0,
      "end_time": 1048960.0,
      "text": "and the US Department of Justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1048119.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1053138.0,
      "text": "put the number of untested, abandoned rape kits at 400,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1053160.0,
      "end_time": 1054616.0,
      "text": "across this country."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1054640.0,
      "end_time": 1056296.0,
      "text": "Four hundred thousand."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1056320.0,
      "end_time": 1058481.0,
      "text": "That's a national pandemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1059280.0,
      "end_time": 1061495.0,
      "text": "We know where a lot of those kits are."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1061520.0,
      "end_time": 1063216.0,
      "text": "Our testing showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1063240.0,
      "end_time": 1068576.0,
      "text": "that women were raped waiting in their cars, waiting for friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1068600.0,
      "end_time": 1072136.0,
      "text": "on their way to work, on their way from work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1072160.0,
      "end_time": 1074520.0,
      "text": "at gas stations, at shopping malls."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1075680.0,
      "end_time": 1077896.0,
      "text": "And even one of the first cases that we did"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1077920.0,
      "end_time": 1080376.0,
      "text": "when these rape kits were starting to be tested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1080400.0,
      "end_time": 1082616.0,
      "text": "was a man who came into the window"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1082640.0,
      "end_time": 1086800.0,
      "text": "and got into the bed and raped a woman who was in bed with her two children."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1087680.0,
      "end_time": 1090360.0,
      "text": "He raped her while he was in bed with her two children."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1091280.0,
      "end_time": 1095136.0,
      "text": "Every time I look at a rape victim that comes into my office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1095160.0,
      "end_time": 1096816.0,
      "text": "because their case is being called"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1096840.0,
      "end_time": 1099310.0,
      "text": "or they're being interviewed by the prosecutor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1099550.0,
      "end_time": 1100616.0,
      "text": "they are being prepped for case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1100640.0,
      "end_time": 1102760.0,
      "text": "I look into their eyes and I think to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1103760.0,
      "end_time": 1106336.0,
      "text": "they didn't have to be one of the ones that was raped."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1106360.0,
      "end_time": 1108456.0,
      "text": "They didn't have to be one of those victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1108480.0,
      "end_time": 1112880.0,
      "text": "And maybe they would not have been, if these rape kits had been tested timely."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1115120.0,
      "end_time": 1118159.0,
      "text": "How many more Pamelas are in this world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1119360.0,
      "end_time": 1122656.0,
      "text": "How many more Natashas are in this world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1122680.0,
      "end_time": 1124136.0,
      "text": "We may never know."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1124160.0,
      "end_time": 1127416.0,
      "text": "But what I do know is that you have the technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1127440.0,
      "end_time": 1128656.0,
      "text": "you know how to use it"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1128680.0,
      "end_time": 1133000.0,
      "text": "and you can help us solve the problem of rape kits being stockpiled."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1133560.0,
      "end_time": 1134856.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1134880.0,
      "end_time": 1141600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}